{"tid":1158762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"自私家長疑為泊車　出動女兒霸錶位　車友：唔敢爭","createTime":"2019-05-17T07:57:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T08:18:47.000Z","uid":225464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9ee1a49b59be57574d4b9456f1b0b2793d1f2397","tid":1158762,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T07:57:00.000Z","msg":"自私家長疑為泊車 出動女兒霸錶位 車友：唔敢爭<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2QbofLl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2QbofLl&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEXxYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=82118d6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2QbofLl</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190517/photo/bkn-20190517152900407-0517_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190517155410\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190517%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190517152900407-0517_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190517155410&h=4ceafa71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n父母真係咁放心？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為得一個泊車錶位，司機們都會絞盡腦汁。近日屯門就有女孩上演「人肉霸位」，乖乖站着守護車位，震驚不少網民︰「邊敢同你爭」。<br />\n<br />\n從Facebook群組「馬路的事討論區」的相片可見，有女童晚上獨自呆站在藍地大街一個咪錶位上，疑等候家長前來泊車。發貼者斥謂︰「原來依家要出動埋小朋友去人肉霸位，點夠你玩呀！」<br />\n<br />\n網民紛紛批評家長罔顧女童安全︰「要小朋友企喺馬路上咁危險」、「小朋友嘅高度，真係倒車睇唔到好危險」、「要我個小朋友去霸位，我寧願唔泊」、「我認輸喇，你泊啦」。"},{"pid":"9c8b455f3a5a95b8149709710b991f9a701f577c","tid":1158762,"uid":192581,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T08:02:28.000Z","msg":"其實可能係編輯已經無嘢可以寫 逼自己個女黎幫手作故仔"},{"pid":"301cc2f599b0501527bc57f77c698392f68b2f01","tid":1158762,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9c8b455f3a5a95b8149709710b991f9a701f577c","tid":1158762,"uid":192581,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T08:02:28.000Z","msg":"其實可能係編輯已經無嘢可以寫 逼自己個女黎幫手作故仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T08:03:41.000Z","msg":"可能你就係個編輯嘅仇人，屈個編輯呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10c2e803291c22d0ff9aa4d2e9ff93de0d1070a0","tid":1158762,"uid":225464,"